This tab allows defining people invited to the meeting, actual attendees and people who are excused.
Also permits defining recipients for the Notification email. 

Fields

[emph]Invited[/emph]

Multiple Select box: people who is invited to the meeting.


[emph]Attending[/emph]

Multiple Select box: who are going to attend, or have attended the meeting.


[emph]Excused[/emph]

Multiple Select box: people who is not going or have not attended the meeting.


[emph]Recipients[/emph]

Multiple Select box: email recipients for the Notification.
